      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "An Audience With the Queen",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "I would like to hunt together\r\nsome more, to get a feeling\r\nfor each other\u0027s abilities.\r\nOn that note, I\u0027ve received a\r\nrequest to hunt a Rathian on\r\nthe Sandy Plains. Let\u0027s hone\r\nour teamwork to a fine point!",
